name: Paris the city for lovers
description:
They say: "Paris is a city for lovers." 
Well lets discuss where this rumor/belief had been come into being.
There was a neighbourhood in Paris in 1930's called "le duel" in which lovers used to duel to win the mistress.
They say that the pavement and the walls of that neighbourhood was turned to red beacuase of blood of miserable lovers.
This artwork was illustrated to make this story retained. The duality is evidently and repeatedly used in this artwork to power the story
